  • Field Details

    • yBackprop

      public final Operand<T extends TNumber> yBackprop
      A 4D Tensor for the gradient with respect to y.

    • x

      public final Operand<T extends TNumber> x
      A 4D Tensor for input data.

    • scale

      public final Operand<TFloat32> scale
      A 1D Tensor for scaling factor, to scale the normalized x.

    • reserveSpace1

      public final Operand<U extends TNumber> reserveSpace1
      When is_training is True, a 1D Tensor for the computed batch mean to be reused in gradient computation. When is_training is False, a 1D Tensor for the population mean to be reused in both 1st and 2nd order gradient computation.

    • reserveSpace2

      public final Operand<U extends TNumber> reserveSpace2
      When is_training is True, a 1D Tensor for the computed batch variance (inverted variance in the cuDNN case) to be reused in gradient computation. When is_training is False, a 1D Tensor for the population variance to be reused in both 1st and 2nd order gradient computation.

    • reserveSpace3

      public final Operand<U extends TNumber> reserveSpace3
      When is_training is True, a 1D Tensor for some intermediate results to be reused in gradient computation. When is_training is False, a dummy empty Tensor will be created.

    • T

      public final DataType T
      The data type for the elements of input and output Tensors.

    • U

      public final DataType U
      The data type for the scale, offset, mean, and variance.

    • epsilon

      public final float epsilon
      A small float number added to the variance of x.

    • dataFormat

      public final String dataFormat
      The data format for y_backprop, x, x_backprop. Either "NHWC" (default) or "NCHW".

    • isTraining

      public final boolean isTraining
      A bool value to indicate the operation is for training (default) or inference.
